    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used car market. The exterior is flawless, showing absolutely no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections of any kind; the finish gleams as if freshly off the showroom floor. The interior is equally pristine, with spotless upholstery, fully functional controls, and no signs of wear on any surfaces. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with all mechanical components in top working order. All electronics, lights, and safety systems operate perfectly. This is an outstanding opportunity for a buyer seeking a used vehicle that looks and performs like new \u2014 you will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 45000.0,
