      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and offers a reliable, well-maintained option for buyers looking for quality transportation at a fair price. The exterior presents nicely, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 no dents, rust, or significant paint damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, showing modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort. Mechanically, the car runs well; all major systems are in good working order, and it has been regularly serviced. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and all lights and electronics function as expected. This is an honest, solid used car \u2014 not perfect, but genuinely well cared for and ready to drive.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. There is minor cosmetic wear \u2014 small scratches or light paint blemishes \u2014 consistent with normal use, but no rust or major damage. The interior is intact and functional. A solid, dependable used vehicle.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Great Condition & Ready to Go \u2014 Solid Value at an Honest Price! \ud83c\udf1f If you're looking for a well-maintained car that delivers real quality without the mint-condition price tag, this is it! This vehicle is in genuinely good condition \u2014 it looks great, drives smoothly, and has been well cared for over its life. You'll notice the interior is clean and comfortable, and everything functions as it should. There may be minor signs of normal use here and there, but nothing that takes away from the overall excellent experience of owning and driving this car. A smart buy for anyone who wants quality and reliability without going to the top of the market! \ud83d\ude97",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_4",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition with significant wear and mechanical issues, best suited for parts or a buyer prepared to invest in repairs.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
